snippet.title: PracticalMachinist
snippet.description: Practical Machinist is the largest manufacturing forum on the web - A vibrant community of dedicated machinists, fabricators, engineers and manufacturers from all industries and interests. This channel was created to host video content that can be viewed here or on our forum. Comments, questions and discussion about these videos can be found there. Please visit http://practicalmachinist.com to join the conversation.
